flowchart TD
    Trigger["EventBridge fires every 3h<br/>Kafka delivers 90-day data across 10 client portfolios"]
    Trigger --> Supervisor

    subgraph PerClient["Per client (x10) - Supervisor iterates, once per rule that client has"]
        Supervisor["Supervisor<br/>query Rules KB for this client<br/>-> applicable_rules (e.g. 5 rules)"]
        Dispatcher["Rule Dispatcher<br/>validate / order rules"]
        Gate["MoE Gate<br/>per rule, decide which subagents to call"]
        DataAgent["Data Agent<br/>MATURE cohort (>45d old)<br/>Metrics/Schema KB -> SQL -> Redshift<br/>-> BaselineMatrix"]
        FeatureAgent["Feature Curation Agent<br/>RECENT cohort (under 40d)<br/>same maturity-band shape<br/>-> CuratedFeatures"]
        Comparison["Comparison Agent<br/>lag_mult x trend_mult<br/>-> Base / Trended / Stress projection<br/>+ separate profile-shift signal"]
        StatTest["Statistical Testing Agent<br/>severity threshold check<br/>-> CRITICAL / HIGH / MEDIUM"]
        Signal["Real-Time Signal Agent<br/>packages one alert-ready signal"]

        Supervisor --> Dispatcher --> Gate
        Gate --> DataAgent
        Gate --> FeatureAgent
        DataAgent --> Comparison
        FeatureAgent --> Comparison
        Comparison --> StatTest --> Signal
    end

    Note["repeat this block for each rule,<br/>then for clients B through J (10 total)"]
    Signal -.-> Note

    Signal --> Aggregate["Aggregate across all 10 clients' signals<br/>this cross-portfolio rollup is the actual trend"]
    Aggregate --> Cache["Write into AWS KB cache"]
    Cache --> LLM["Detection Agent / Deep Analysis Agent<br/>ONLY LLM-based, ReAct agents<br/>reason across the cross-portfolio trend"]

    style LLM fill:#e0edff,stroke:#2563eb,stroke-width:2px
    style Note fill:#ffffff,stroke:#cccccc,stroke-dasharray: 5 5